Psalm 83-9 <pb/><t>Do to them as you did to <f>ⓢ</f>Midian, </t><t>as to <f>ⓣ</f>Sisera and Jabin at <f>ⓤ</f>the river Kishon,</t>
Psalm 83-10 <t>who were destroyed at <f>ⓥ</f>En-dor, </t><t>who became <f>ⓦ</f>dung for the ground.</t>
